<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rome</title>

    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/favicon/apple-touch-icon.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon/favicon-32x32.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon/favicon-16x16.png">
    <meta name="msapplication-TileColor" content="#da532c">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#ffffff">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/Stylesheets/css_home/libs.bundle.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/Stylesheets/css_home/theme.bundle.css">

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #111111;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        nav.navbar {
            background-color: transparent !important;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav.navbar .nav-link,
        nav.navbar .navbar-brand {
            color: #ffffff !important;
        }

        nav.navbar:hover {
            background-color: #ffffff !important;
        }

        nav.navbar:hover .nav-link,
        nav.navbar:hover .navbar-brand {
            color: #000000 !important;
        }

        .rome-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 150px auto 50px auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 40px;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .rome-image {
            flex: 0 0 300px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .rome-image img {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .rome-text {
            flex: 1;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #ccc;
        }

        .rome-video {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
        }

        .rome-video iframe {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        .wanttogo-btn button {
            border: 2px solid #5d3eff;
            color: #5d3eff;
            background: transparent;
            padding: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .wanttogo-btn button:hover {
            background-color: #5d3eff;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg border-0 position-absolute top-0 start-0 w-100 z-index-30">
    <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center flex-wrap">
        <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold fs-3 m-0 p-0" href="/home">Rome</a>

        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNavDropdown">
            <ul class="navbar-nav mx-auto">
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/home">Home</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/wanttogo">Want To Go</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                    <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">Categories</a>
                    <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                        <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/hiking">Hiking</a></li>
                        <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/islands">Islands</a></li>
                        <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/cities">Cities</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<div class="rome-content">
    <div class="rome-image">
        <img src="/images/rome.png" alt="Rome">

        <!-- Fixed backend form -->
        <form method="POST" action="/want-to-go" class="wanttogo-btn">
            <input type="hidden" name="slug" value="rome">
            <button type="submit">Add to Want to Go</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div class="rome-text">
        <p>
            Rome today is one of the most important tourist destinations in the world, due to the immense archaeological and art treasures,
            the charm of its unique traditions, the beauty of its panoramic views, and the majesty of its magnificent villas.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rome-video">
        <iframe height="315"
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GXoEpNjgKzg?si=mw2WByO-sxV2MQjw"
                title="Rome video"
                frameborder="0"
                allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="/javascript/js_home/vendor.bundle.js"></script>
<script src="/javascript/js_home/theme.bundle.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
